Package com.gemalto.idp.mobile.otp.dsformatting.primitive

Interface GroupedInputDialogPrimitive

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InputDialogPrimitive, InputPrimitive, Primitive
    public interface GroupedInputDialogPrimitive
extends InputDialogPrimitive
    An interface representing a grouped input dialog (IDG) primitive.

    This is an extension of the InputDialogPrimitive which visually partition the input into groups. e.g. 1234 5678.

    This primitive has type Primitive.PrimitiveType.IDG.

    The allowed input format is InputPrimitive.InputFormat.DIGIT.
